                    License along with this program (COPYING file in extension root); if not, write to the Free Software
                    Foundation, Inc., 51 Franklin Street, Fifth Floor, Boston, MA  02110-1301 USA.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
{/block}
